{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Create a new Ombudsman and protections for owners of new build homes",
        "additional_details": "The Ombudsman should have powers to compel developers to remedy faults, and order compensation for inconvenience, stress and financial loss.\r\n \r\nDevelopers should be required to arrange a deposit for all new build properties, which is at risk if there are issues with the property.",
        "background": "The Government should create a new Ombudsman to look at all complaints regarding new build homes that are still under warranty for building defects, and impose additional requirements for developers or new builds properties.",
